data.description: Updated ranch style home with an amazing view of Pikes Peak. Easy maintenance Xeriscaped front yard with cobblestone walkway. Imagine enjoying your morning coffee or evening beverage on the deck with absolutely stunning views. Upon entry you will fall in the love with the open floor plan with lots of flex space to meet your needs. The upgraded kitchen is a chef’s delight with plenty of cabinet and counter space. You will love the stainless double oven. The gas cook top sits in a beautiful granite island. LVP flooring for easy clean up. Check out the beautiful glass tile backsplash. There is main level office space and a full bath. You will appreciate the fantastic owner’s suite with en-suite bath and laundry area. Outside is a small shed and fire pit. Downstairs are 4 bedrooms, a full bath and a second laundry room. Lots of storage in the over sized garage and crawlspace. Great central location close to everything Colorado Springs has to offer.
